        <item>
            <title>Version 1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 21:13:22 -0500</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Trivia Master: shares genuine, surprising facts related to what's on screen</li>                    <li>Barfly Know-It-All: delivers completely fabricated trivia with absolute confidence (Cliff Clavin-style)</li>                    <li>Now-playing awareness: Servo detects what you're listening to in Spotify or Apple Music and weaves it into its commentary</li>                    <li>Holiday awareness: Servo acknowledges upcoming and current US holidays in its observations</li>                    <li>Gemma 4 support: switched to the /api/chat API to fix image handling and hangs on Apple Silicon when using Ollama with Gemma 4 models; timeout increased to 120s for large models</li>                    <li>Speech balloon positioning is tighter: bubble sits closer to the screen edge and the tail tip now reaches the pet emoji</li>                    <li>Improved robustness when screen state changes rapidly</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
